{"id":688514,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/688514.html","date":"2022-10-17T16:28:18Z","modified":"2022-10-17T16:29:04Z","title":"【CDTV】中国多地学生被要求观看二十大开幕式直播","content":"<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"【CDTV】中国多地学生被要求观看二十大开幕式直播\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2No5WQlkSDA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>10月16日，中国共产党第二十次全国代表大会开幕。一些在中文互联网上流传的群聊截图显示，中国多地学校要求学生观看二十大开幕式直播。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/10/截屏2022-10-17-15.08.11.png\" alt=\"image\" /><span style=\"font-size: 0.8em;color: #666;display: block;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 20px;line-height: 22px;\">某地幼儿园要求学生观看二十大开幕式直播</span>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/10/截屏2022-10-17-15.07.31.png\" alt=\"image\" /><span style=\"font-size: 0.8em;color: #666;display: block;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 20px;line-height: 22px;\">某地小学要求学生观看二十大开幕式直播</span>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/10/截屏2022-10-17-15.07.06.png\" alt=\"image\" /><span style=\"font-size: 0.8em;color: #666;display: block;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 20px;line-height: 22px;\">某地高中组织学生观看二十大开幕式直播</span>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/10/截屏2022-10-17-15.07.53.png\" alt=\"image\" /><span style=\"font-size: 0.8em;color: #666;display: block;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 20px;line-height: 22px;\">某大学要求学生观看二十大开幕式直播</span>\n<p>在一些流传的视频中也显示，多地学校组织学生集体观看开幕式直播。</p>\n<div style=\"width:100%;margin:0 auto;padding-left:20px\">\n<div class=\"su-spoiler su-spoiler-style-fancy su-spoiler-icon-chevron-circle su-spoiler-closed\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\" data-anchor-in-url=\"no\"><div class=\"su-spoiler-title\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"su-spoiler-icon\"></span>CDT 档案卡</div><div class=\"su-spoiler-content su-u-clearfix su-u-t